Using Recurrence Relation for nCr
The recurrence relation for nCr is C(i,k) = C(i-1,k-1) + C(i-1,k).
Thus we can calculate nCr in time complexity O(n*r) and space complexity O(n*r).
https://comeoncodeon.wordpress.com/category/algorithm/

